{"meta":{"title":"2 Nefi 14","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/14?lang=spa","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ/2017-11-0360-2-nephi-14-64k-spa.mp3?download=true","voice":{"name":"audio"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"20c77fb6e7bd3f58f841e0b5c3923229e53391ef","data-aid":"124165604","data-aid-version":"3","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/14","itemscope":"","itemtype":"http://schema.org/Article","lang":"spa","data-orig-id":"aad669ae4a699b9a203f7fc9917f29ecfb153d79","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"2 Nefi 14","description":"Sion y sus hijas serán redimidas y purificadas en el día milenario — Compárese con Isaías 4. Aproximadamente 559–545 a.C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"2 Nefi 14","description":"Sion y sus hijas serán redimidas y purificadas en el día milenario — Compárese con Isaías 4. Aproximadamente 559–545 a.C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"124165612\" id=\"title_number1\">Capítulo 14</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"124165617\" id=\"study_summary1\">Sion y sus hijas serán redimidas y purificadas en el día milenario — Compárese con <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/4?lang=spa\">Isaías 4</a>. Aproximadamente 559–545 a.C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124165622\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>Y en aquel día siete mujeres echarán mano de un hombre, diciendo: Nuestro propio pan comeremos, y con nuestra propia ropa nos vestiremos; tan solo déjanos llevar tu nombre para quitar nuestro <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>oprobio</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124165625\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>En aquel día el <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>renuevo</a> del Señor será bello y glorioso, y el fruto de la tierra excelente y hermoso para los de Israel que hayan escapado.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124165629\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Y acontecerá que los que fueren dejados en Sion, y los que quedaren en Jerusalén, serán llamados santos, todos los que en Jerusalén estén inscritos entre los vivientes,</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124165633\" id=\"p4\"><span class=\"verse-number\">4 </span><a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>cuando</a> el Señor haya <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>lavado</a> la inmundicia de las hijas de Sion, y limpiado la sangre de Jerusalén de en medio de ella con espíritu de juicio y con espíritu de <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>ardimiento</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124165634\" id=\"p5\"><span class=\"verse-number\">5 </span>Y creará el Señor, sobre toda morada del monte de Sion, y sobre sus asambleas, una <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note5a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>nube</a> y humo de día, y resplandor de fuego y llamas de noche, porque sobre toda la gloria de Sion habrá una defensa.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124165637\" id=\"p6\"><span class=\"verse-number\">6 </span>Y habrá un tabernáculo para sombra contra el calor del día, y para <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note6a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>refugio</a> y abrigo contra el turbión y contra el aguacero.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"14\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124165639\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><em>Es decir,</em> el estigma del no haberse casado ni haber tenido hijos.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124165641\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/60.21?lang=spa#p21\">Isa. 60:21</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.5?lang=spa#p5\">2 Ne. 3:5</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.25?lang=spa#p25\">Jacob 2:25</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"4\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note4a\" data-full-marker=\"4a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124165643\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><em>Es decir,</em> cuando el Señor haya purificado la tierra.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note4b\" data-full-marker=\"4b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124165645\" id=\"note4b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/wash-washed-washings?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Lavado, lavamientos, lavar</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note4c\" data-full-marker=\"4c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124165649\" id=\"note4c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/3.2-3?lang=spa#p2\">Mal. 3:2–3</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/4.1?lang=spa#p1\">4:1</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"5\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note5a\" data-full-marker=\"5a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124165652\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ex/13.21?lang=spa#p21\">Éx. 13:21</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"6\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note6a\" data-full-marker=\"6a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124165655\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/25.4?lang=spa#p4\">Isa. 25:4</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/115.6?lang=spa#p6\">DyC 115:6</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note1a":{"id":"note1a","marker":"1a","pid":"124165622","context":"oprobio","text":"<p data-aid=\"124165639\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><em>Es decir,</em> el estigma del no haberse casado ni haber tenido hijos.</p>"},"note2a":{"id":"note2a","marker":"2a","pid":"124165625","context":"renuevo","text":"<p data-aid=\"124165641\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/60.21?lang=spa#p21\">Isa. 60:21</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.5?lang=spa#p5\">2 Ne. 3:5</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.25?lang=spa#p25\">Jacob 2:25</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/60.21?lang=spa#p21","text":"Isa. 60:21"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.5?lang=spa#p5","text":"2 Ne. 3:5"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.25?lang=spa#p25","text":"Jacob 2:25"}]},"note4a":{"id":"note4a","marker":"4a","pid":"124165633","context":"cuando","text":"<p data-aid=\"124165643\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><em>Es decir,</em> cuando el Señor haya purificado la tierra.</p>"},"note4b":{"id":"note4b","marker":"4b","pid":"124165633","context":"lavado","text":"<p data-aid=\"124165645\" id=\"note4b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/wash-washed-washings?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Lavado, lavamientos, lavar</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/wash-washed-washings?lang=spa","text":"GEE Lavado, lavamientos, lavar"}]},"note4c":{"id":"note4c","marker":"4c","pid":"124165633","context":"ardimiento","text":"<p data-aid=\"124165649\" id=\"note4c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/3.2-3?lang=spa#p2\">Mal. 3:2–3</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/4.1?lang=spa#p1\">4:1</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/3.2-3?lang=spa#p2","text":"Mal. 3:2–3"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/4.1?lang=spa#p1","text":"4:1"}]},"note5a":{"id":"note5a","marker":"5a","pid":"124165634","context":"nube","text":"<p data-aid=\"124165652\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ex/13.21?lang=spa#p21\">Éx. 13:21</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/ex/13.21?lang=spa#p21","text":"Éx. 13:21"}]},"note6a":{"id":"note6a","marker":"6a","pid":"124165637","context":"refugio","text":"<p data-aid=\"124165655\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/25.4?lang=spa#p4\">Isa. 25:4</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/115.6?lang=spa#p6\">DyC 115:6</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/25.4?lang=spa#p4","text":"Isa. 25:4"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/115.6?lang=spa#p6","text":"DyC 115:6"}]}}},"pids":[["124165604",{"key":"124165604"}],["124165612",{"key":"124165612"}],["124165617",{"key":"124165617"}],["124165622",{"key":"124165622"}],["124165625",{"key":"124165625"}],["124165629",{"key":"124165629"}],["124165633",{"key":"124165633"}],["124165634",{"key":"124165634"}],["124165637",{"key":"124165637"}],["124165639",{"key":"124165639"}],["124165641",{"key":"124165641"}],["124165643",{"key":"124165643"}],["124165645",{"key":"124165645"}],["124165649",{"key":"124165649"}],["124165652",{"key":"124165652"}],["124165655",{"key":"124165655"}]],"tableOfContentsUri":"/scriptures/bofm","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/14"}